{"TopicId":154535,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"3,75m or even bigger command pods","CreatedByName":"michal.don","CreatedById":150623,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-05T13:09:02Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"michal.don","CreatedById":150623,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-05T13:09:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCould you please suggest a mod that adds command pods/crew pods with more crew capacity that fit nicely on 3,75m rockets, or even larger ones? I love to use SpaceY\u00A0parts that are 5m and 7,5m, so it desn\u0027t look very good if the huge rocket has a hitchhiker and a Mk2 pod on the top of it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMichal.don\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gianni1122","CreatedById":170752,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-05T15:08:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/150623-michaldon/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022150623\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/150623-michaldon/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@michal.don\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCheck out TweakScale. It won\u0027t change capacity of pods but it can certainly help make\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Ea lot\u00A0\u003C/em\u003Eof things \u0022fit\u00A0nicely\u0022.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/101540-122-tweakscale-v233dec-17/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DStaal","CreatedById":155685,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-05T16:53:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRather than reposting what I said before, I\u0027ll just point you to a previous discussion that touched on this:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcon